library(tsibble)
library(tsibbledata)
library(tidyverse)
library(lubridate)

##tsibble index : time component key : identifies the underlying structure of the data & uniquely identifies each row

interval(vic_elec)

<interval[1]>
[1] 30m
vic_elec %>% 
  select(Time, Demand, Temperature)
vic_elec %>% 
  filter_index("2012-01")

##tsibble and ggplot

vic_elec %>% 
  filter(!Holiday) %>% 
  ggplot()+
  geom_line(aes(x = Time,
                y = Temperature))

floor_date()
ceiling_date()

yearweek()
yearmonth()
yearquarter()

##rolling windows

library(slider)
library(feasts)
elec_rolling <- vic_elec %>% 
  mutate(
    temp_moving_avg = slide_dbl(
      .x = Temperature,
      .f = ~mean(.x, na.rm = TRUE),
      .before = 1000,
      .after = 1000,
      .complete = FALSE
    )
  )
ggplot(elec_rolling)+
  geom_line(aes(x = Date, y = Temperature), colour = "grey")+
  geom_line(aes(x = Date, y = temp_moving_avg), colour = "red")
